
<!DOCTYPE svg PUBLIC “-//W3C//DTD SVG 1.1//EN”
“http://www.w3.org/Graphics/SVG/1.1/DTD/svg11.dtd”> 

<head>
    <meta http-equiv='Content-Type' content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' />
    <link rel='stylesheet' href='https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.3.1/css/bootstrap.min.css' integrity='sha384-ggOyR0iXCbMQv3Xipma34MD+dH/1fQ784/j6cY/iJTQUOhcWr7x9JvoRxT2MZw1T' crossorigin='anonymous'>
    <link rel='stylesheet' href='https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/bootstrap-select/1.13.1/css/bootstrap-select.min.css'>
    <link rel= 'stylesheet' href='/static/css/style_home.css' />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, shrink-to-fit=no">
    <%- include includes/scripts_env.ejs %>
</head>

<body>

    <header>
        <div id='banner'>
            <p id ='titre'>DATA VISUALTION</p>
        </div>
    </header>
    
    <div id='general-menu'>
        <a href='/generator' class='nav-link' id='generator'>Generator</a>       
        <div class ='card card-body bg-light'><p style='font-weight: bold'>Estimation des émissions de CO2 </p><p><br> Dues à la combustion de combustibles fossiles, à la production de ciment et au gaz brûlés à la torchère. En milliers de tonnes de dioxyde de carbone pour les
        pays ou/et en tonne par habitant</p>
    </div>  

    <div class ='container'> 
        <div class ='row'>
            <div id='legend' class ='col'></div>
        </div>
        <div class ='row' id='subject'>
            <div class="col-lg-4" id="side">
                <div id="row">
                    <div id='vis' class='row'> </div>
                    <div class ='row main-menu'>
                        <div id='controls-continent' class="col" >
                            <div class="custom-control custom-radio">
                                <input type="radio" class="custom-control-input radio-choice" id="byContinent" name="choice"  checked>
                                <label class="custom-control-label" for="byContinent">Par Continent</label>
                            </div>
                            <select class='selectpicker sContinent' data-live-search='true' title='Choose' id='selectContinent' >
                                <optgroup label='Continent' id='Continent'>
                                    <option id='Asie' class = 'option-continent' value='1' >Asie</option>
                                    <option id='Africa' class = 'option-continent' value='2'>Africa</option>
                                    <option id='Europe' class = 'option-continent' value='3' selected>Europe</option>
                                    <option id='NorthAmerica' class = 'option-continent' value='4'>North America</option>
                                    <option id='SouthAmerica' class = 'option-continent' value='5'>South America</option>
                                    <option id='Oceania' class = 'option-continent' value='6'>Oceania</option>
                                </optgroup>
                            </select>
                            <div class="custom-control custom-radio " style='text-align: none'>
                                <input type="radio" class="custom-control-input radio-choice" id="byCountry" name="choice">
                                <label class="custom-control-label" for="byCountry">Par pays</label>
                            </div>
                            <select class='selectpicker scountry' multiple data-live-search='true' id='selectCountry' >
                                <optgroup label='Pays' id='Pays' data-max-options='10' >
                                </optgroup>
                            </select>
                            <div class="custom-control custom-radio " style='text-align: none'>
                                <input type="radio" class="custom-control-input radio-choice" id="Top10" name="choice">
                                <label class="custom-control-label" for="Top10">Top 10</label>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class ='row'>
                        <div id='timeLine' class='col'>
                            <button id='play-button'> Play </button>
                        </div>
                    </div>
            
                    <div class ='row'>
                        <div id ='zoom-button' class='zoom  col'>
                            <p class ="text-zoom" style="display: inline; padding-right: 10px;" > Zoom</p>
                            <button id='button-moins'>-</button>
                            <button id='button-plus'>+</button>                              
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class ='row'>
                        <div class="col" style='text-align: center;'> 
                            <div class="custom-control custom-radio custom-inline">
                                <input type="radio" class="custom-control-input radio-t menu-input" id="total" name="pollu"  checked>
                                <label class="custom-control-label" for="total">Pollution par pays</label>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class = 'row'>
                        <div class="col" style='text-align: center;'> 
                            <div class="custom-control custom-radio custom-inline">
                                <input type="radio" class="custom-control-input radio-t menu-input" id="per-capita" name="pollu">
                                <label class="custom-control-label" for="per-capita">Pollution par habitants</label>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class ='row'>
                        <div class='col'>
                            <h3> Choix de la représentation</h3>
                            <div class ="main-img">
                                <div class ="img">
                                    <img class ="image" src="/static/img/BubbleChart.png" style="margin-bottom: 10px;">
                                    <div class="custom-control custom-radio">
                                        <input type="radio" class="custom-control-input radio-rp" id="bubble" name="repres" checked>
                                        <label class="custom-control-label" for="bubble">Bubble Chart</label>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="img">
                                    <img class ="image custom-inline" src="/static/img/Graph.png">
                                    <div class="custom-control custom-radio">
                                        <input type="radio" class="custom-control-input radio-rp" id="graph" name="repres" >
                                        <label class="custom-control-label" for="graph">Graph</label>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div id='chart' class = 'col-lg-8'></div>
        </div>
    </div>        
                       
    <script type='module' src='/static/js/pollution/main.js'></script>
    
</body>
</html>

